<div class="email-container">
  <h1>EGYM Genius – Here's What's New!</h1>
<img alt="Header Image" class="header-image" src="https://de.egym.com/sites/default/files/2025-05/HeroMedium_LP_GENIUS_EN_mobilex2.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto;"/>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tr><td style="border-top: 1px solid #ffffff; padding: 10px 0;"></td></tr>
</table>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">    
We’re excited to share the latest EGYM Genius improvements with you. Here’s a quick overview of what’s been improved since our last update.<br/><br/>Note: To see these updates, please ensure the BMA and/or the Trainer App is up to date.
 <br/>
 <br/>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tr><td style="border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; padding: 10px 0;"></td></tr>
</table>
  <h2>More balanced training plans
</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
We have improved our Genius AI to distribute weekly training volume more effectively across movements and muscle groups. This introduces greater exercise variety and aligns more closely with each member’s goals and experience level. The result is higher‑quality, personalized training plans that make the most of your gym inventory.<br/>
 <br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/egym-genius-plans.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <br/>
  <h2>Genius for Members: Smart exercise replacement</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
If a member wants to replace an exercise in a given workout, Genius now recommends suitable alternatives that still target the intended training stimulus and goal. Members can swap exercises instantly, getting a training plan adapted to their needs in seconds.<br/><br/>
  <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/egym-genius-replace-exercise.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <br/>
  <h2>Genius for Trainers: See when a plan is being updated</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
We’ve made the way EGYM Genius updates training plans more transparent. The UI now more clearly shows when a training plan is being updated and when it’s ready to use, so that personal trainers always know what Genius is doing, and can continue coaching, stay focused, and maintain a professional presence on the gym floor.
 <br/> <br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/genius-ui-updating.gif" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <br/>
    <h2>Optimized logic for exercise guidance videos in custom exercise libraries</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
New logic ensures that if an operator has a customized activity library but hasn't uploaded a specific video for an exercise, the system will automatically pull the latest high-quality video from the EGYM Master Library. This guarantees that members always see the most up-to-date, high-quality media for their training plan and eliminates "missing media" gaps while still respecting any custom content the club has intentionally uploaded.
 <br/><br/>
      <h2>Inventory management in Business Suite: Faster and more accurate</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
The enhanced equipment imagery for the Functional and Free Weight categories in the Business Suite enables operators to manage their gym‑floor inventory faster and more accurately. Genius now knows exactly which equipment is available, ensuring training plans match your studio setup and members receive a seamless experience.
 <br/><br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/business-suite-inventory.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>

